WEBVTT	#Elemental Media Engine(TM) 2.17.0.0

00:00:00.00 --> 00:00:00.51


00:00:00.51 --> 00:00:03.15
A young girl who disappeared more than two years ago

00:00:03.15 --> 00:00:05.85
in Central New York has been found alive.

00:00:05.85 --> 00:00:09.90
Police found Paislee Shultis in this secret compartment

00:00:09.90 --> 00:00:13.77
under the stairs in a home that they had searched before.

00:00:13.77 --> 00:00:15.27
Officials say the little girl was

00:00:15.27 --> 00:00:17.34
abducted by her biological parents

00:00:17.34 --> 00:00:19.52
after they lost custody of her.

00:00:19.52 --> 00:00:21.27
Our National Correspondant, Jericka Duncan

00:00:21.27 --> 00:00:25.17
shows us now, how one detective paying very close attention

00:00:25.17 --> 00:00:28.01
made the startling discovery.

00:00:28.01 --> 00:00:31.25
After two years of searching, detectives finally

00:00:31.25 --> 00:00:35.33
found Paislee Shulits in this home in Saugerties, New York,

00:00:35.33 --> 00:00:39.23
huddled in a small wet space beneath the staircase.

00:00:39.23 --> 00:00:40.91
One of my detectives was--

00:00:40.91 --> 00:00:43.04
walked up and down the steps a number of times

00:00:43.04 --> 00:00:44.54
during the course of the search.

00:00:44.54 --> 00:00:46.04
And he said there was just something

00:00:46.04 --> 00:00:48.05
about the steps that was off.

00:00:48.05 --> 00:00:50.75
He used a flashlight and where two of the step boards

00:00:50.75 --> 00:00:52.91
came together, he looked through the crack

00:00:52.91 --> 00:00:54.95
and he saw what he believed was a blanket.

00:00:54.95 --> 00:00:57.05
Eventually, they saw a pair of little feet

00:00:57.05 --> 00:00:58.70
and when they got more boards off,

00:00:58.70 --> 00:01:00.95
they found the little girl Paislee.

00:01:00.95 --> 00:01:04.52
The girl, now six years old, was discovered with her mother

00:01:04.52 --> 00:01:05.78
Kimberly Cooper.

00:01:05.78 --> 00:01:09.08
Police believe Cooper and the girl's father, Kirk Shultis,

00:01:09.08 --> 00:01:14.27
Jr. kidnapped Paislee, after losing custody of her in 2019.

00:01:14.27 --> 00:01:17.15
Investigators had been to the home before.

00:01:17.15 --> 00:01:19.79
It belonged to the girl's paternal grandfather.

00:01:19.79 --> 00:01:21.98
But investigators say a fresh tip

00:01:21.98 --> 00:01:23.99
led them to believe the child was being

00:01:23.99 --> 00:01:25.73
hidden inside the residence.

00:01:25.73 --> 00:01:29.27
On Monday, officers arrived with a search warrant.

00:01:29.27 --> 00:01:31.73
They were adamant with our officers

00:01:31.73 --> 00:01:33.47
that the child was not there, which

00:01:33.47 --> 00:01:35.42
led me to believe after the fact,

00:01:35.42 --> 00:01:38.15
that they had done this so many times and gotten away with it.

00:01:38.15 --> 00:01:41.63
Both biological parents, along with Paisley's grandfather,

00:01:41.63 --> 00:01:44.67
were arrested and are now facing several charges,

00:01:44.67 --> 00:01:47.21
including endangering the welfare of a child.

00:01:47.21 --> 00:01:50.42
Paislee is in good health and was reunited with her older

00:01:50.42 --> 00:01:52.55
sister and legal guardian.

00:01:52.55 --> 00:01:57.53
For CBS Mornings, Jericka Duncan, New York.

00:01:57.53 --> 00:01:58.64
It's a very ugly story.

00:01:58.64 --> 00:02:00.68
The police also said that the little girl had not

00:02:00.68 --> 00:02:02.03
been taught to read or write.

00:02:02.03 --> 00:02:02.85
She's now 6.

00:02:02.85 --> 00:02:04.52
And if you have ever had a six-year-old,

00:02:04.52 --> 00:02:06.81
it's not easy to get them to do anything, let alone get

00:02:06.81 --> 00:02:09.20
under a stair and then be hammered in

00:02:09.20 --> 00:02:11.30
and then stay quiet, that's not a pretty picture.

00:02:11.30 --> 00:02:13.45
I'm curious to know why they lost custody.

00:02:13.45 --> 00:02:14.99
Stories of missing kids usually don't

00:02:14.99 --> 00:02:16.34
end with them being found.

00:02:16.34 --> 00:02:18.26
She is safe and alive, we're happy about that.

00:02:18.26 --> 00:02:20.23
That is awesome news.